### Base
@api = http://localhost:3001/api

### Auth
POST {{api}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Health
GET {{api}}/health

### Ready
GET {{api}}/readyz

### Products
GET {{api}}/products

### Admin Stats (use token)
GET {{api}}/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Forum list
GET {{api}}/forum/posts?page=1&pageSize=10&search=

### Create forum post (user token)
POST {{api}}/forum/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "user_uid": "demo-user-uid",
  "title": "Hello",
  "content": "First post"
}

### Messages
GET {{api}}/messages/thread?user_uid=demo-user-uid&peer_uid=seller-user-uid
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

POST {{api}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "sender_uid": "demo-user-uid",
  "receiver_uid": "seller-user-uid",
  "body": "Hi seller"
}